    "title": "Localizing assets in a catalog"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "asset catalogs",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " to organize and manage different types of assets, such as",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "images, sprites, textures, stickers, and data. Most types of assets can have multiple",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "variations to support different device characteristics, including variations for",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the language and region settings.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can localize certain types of asset catalogs and add localized versions of those",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "assets directly to the catalog in Xcode.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The localizable asset types include:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Color sets",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Image sets",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Symbol sets",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Watch complications",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Apple TV image stacks",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sprite atlases",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-asset-catalogs-to-localizations",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add asset catalogs to localizations",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In the Project navigator, select the asset catalog, then select the asset you want",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to localize in the outline view of the editor area. Under Localization in the Attributes",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "inspector, click Localize. Select the localizations you want to add the asset to.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Xcode displays corresponding placeholder spaces in the editor area.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "localizing-assets-in-a-catalog-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Either drop the localized assets in the spaces for localizations, or export the localizations",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and let the localizers add the assets later.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
